des:
Salt Domotics help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your Salt Domotics products.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your Salt Domotics products- just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Salt Domotics products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Salt" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Salt" app;
(3). You need to have some Salt Domotics products in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Salt" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Salt Domotics" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Salt Domotics" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Salt Domotics", and you'll be navigated to "Salt Domotics" login page;
(9). Input your Salt account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on the bedroom light."
"Alexa, turn off the bedroom light."
"Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%."
"Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%."
"Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
